abstract: United States stock indexes regain ground after two-day drop-off in wake of Britain's vote to exit European Union.
lead_paragraph: A new batch of economic data — on home values, consumer confidence and economic growth — helped put traders in a buying mood.

headline.main: Wall St. Rises After Economic and Housing News
